ackground free detection. To prove the performance of the different detector\ncomponents at stratospheric altitudes, a prototype flight will be conducted in\n2011 from Taiki, Japan.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 1 Dec 2010 18:50:19 GMT"}],"update_date":"2010-12-02"}
