on regime, becoming radiatively\ninefficient below a disk luminosity of the order of one per cent of the\nEddington one.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 1 Dec 2010 21:00:04 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 27 Mar 2011 15:14:56 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-20"}
