z factors of Gamma(narrow) >188 and\nGamma(wide) ~18.5. We calculated the beaming-corrected energy release to be 7.9\nx 10^48 erg.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 1 Dec 2010 21:24:19 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-20"}
